########## air ##########

Add To Every object
  Is
    breathable.
End Add To.

The always_here
  Container
End The always_here.


The air Isa object
  In always_here 
End The air.
Verb breath
  Check object Is breathable
    Else 
      "You can't breath $o."
  Does
    "You survive by breathing."
End Verb.


The 'this' Isa location
  
End The 'this'.

Start At 'this'.
  "Breath air!"
  
